tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE Influencers (
    influencer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_name VARCHAR(50),
    total_followers INT,
    collaboration_type VARCHAR(50),
    sponsored_content BOOLEAN,
    partnership_status VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE Influencers (
    influencer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_name VARCHAR(50),
    followers_count INT,
    category VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE Collaborations (
    collaboration_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id UUID,
    blogger_id UUID,
    collaboration_date DATE,
    sponsored_content BOOLEAN,
    partnership_details TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Collaborations (
  collaboration_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  influencer_id INT,
  brand_id INT,
  collaboration_date DATE,
  sponsored_content BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE collaborations (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id INT,
    blogger_id INT,
    collaboration_type VARCHAR(50),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE influencers (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    followers INT NOT NULL,
    website VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE collaborations (
    collab_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id UUID REFERENCES influencers(id),
    brand_id UUID,
    collaboration_date DATE,
    status VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE sponsored_content (
    content_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id UUID REFERENCES influencers(id),
    brand_id UUID,
    content_title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    post_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE partnerships (
    partnership_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id UUID REFERENCES influencers(id),
    brand_id UUID,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE payment (
    payment_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    partnership_id UUID REFERENCES partnerships(partnership_id),
    payment_date DATE,
    amount DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
    payment_status VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
);
